arts.ttl: Netherlands U19’s down Kazakhstan to move into qualifying Elite Round
arts.sum: Netherlands U19s are through to the Elite Round of qualifying for the European Championships after they beat Kazakhstan 2-0. After defeating Ukraine 2-1, Netherlands knew a win would be enough for them to seal a top two spot in the group.
